The paper deals with inverse problems and regularization using denoising algorithms, which are commonly used in image processing and computer vision (cs.CV). The use of denoising algorithms also involves optimization techniques (cs.LG) and numerical analysis (cs.NA). The paper also discusses the application of vector extrapolation, which is a technique commonly used in information theory (cs.IT) and signal processing (cs.SI).
